{"tid":741194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅磡站未來][有片]墨西哥一百貨公司　開幕4個月後倒塌","createTime":"2018-07-13T12:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T14:20:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7a7366c94946a8afd56836edafbc9042f76b2e","tid":741194,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"片:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180713/s00005/1531480291032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180713%2Fs00005%2F1531480291032&d=3e1K2D0rN3D4hsmEee%2Ff3Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0c951b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180713%2Fs00005%2F1531480291032&h=8403fcbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180713/s00005/1531480291032</a><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥一間百貨公司周四（11日）倒塌，從網上短片可見，百貨公司外側的玻璃窗不斷碎裂掉落，整座建築物隨後短短數秒內完全崩塌，露出內部鋼筋結構，現場情況混亂，幸無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n在片段中倒塌的是在墨西哥城的Artz Pedregal商場，位於高速公路旁，事件因此亦影響當日附近交通。《路透社》報道，這間商場本年3月開幕，事隔4個月便完全倒塌，只剩一堆頹垣敗瓦。當局其後封鎖現場調查事發起因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180713/s00005/c0cad2b0f7d4c8846e20d328188fe56d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180713%2Fs00005%2Fc0cad2b0f7d4c8846e20d328188fe56d.jpg&h=ceb508fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca4f3295233c45e3759d017fe3849a42bff34f1a","tid":741194,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d59710e54c25c523bfedfa1be128bbbc459a0bd","tid":741194,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"今日墨西哥, 明日香港"},{"pid":"d887cf91c67c86d8e7c929f5b72811e228d9c2d6","tid":741194,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"急不及待好想睇睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa7b079ad287c65331d2d333c18344de2cb29b9","tid":741194,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"點解拉丁美洲咁多垃圾國家"},{"pid":"f8060ccf06cdbfa3a46ec6d878bb93015684b478","tid":741194,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfa7b079ad287c65331d2d333c18344de2cb29b9","tid":741194,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"點解拉丁美洲咁多垃圾國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"奴隸之後"},{"pid":"1003404d742daea1bd4759fcf117bfee7af6cf82","tid":741194,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/174734_4fd344db436be3f2072774ab99dabfbc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F174734_4fd344db436be3f2072774ab99dabfbc.gif&h=52c28d2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eda5e42ac44bd200f30810e92aa05e831926ea20","tid":741194,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9-TDm-Xk63w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9-TDm-Xk63w&d=3e1K2D0rN3D4hsmEee%2Ff3Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4db2bc29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9-TDm-Xk63w</a><br />\n港版南韓三豐百貨"}]}